snippet: A Chicago-area woman imprisoned in Bali on accusations of killing her mother has given birth to a baby girl, her lawyer said Tuesday.
abstract: Heather Mack, Chicago-area woman imprisoned in Bali on allegations she killed her mother, gives birth to baby girl in Indonesian hospital; she and her boyfriend, Tommy Schaefer, are suspects in death of Sheila von Wiese-Mack whose body was found in suitcase outside a Bali resort.
lead_paragraph: A Chicago-area woman imprisoned in Bali on accusations of killing her mother has given birth to a baby girl, her lawyer said Tuesday.

headline.main: Indonesia: Chicago Woman Held in Mother’s Killing Has a Baby
headline.print_headline: Asia; Indonesia: Chicago Woman Held in Mother’s Killing Has a Baby
